{"type": "article", "id": 27630, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28426, "name": "Prometeo"}, {"id": 28427, "name": "TILE"}, {"id": 28428, "name": "Energysquare"}, {"id": 28429, "name": "Mr O hanger"}, {"id": 28430, "name": "Studio EO"}, {"id": 28431, "name": "NuAns"}, {"id": 28432, "name": "Neri&Hu"}, {"id": 28433, "name": "Paolo D’lppolito"}, {"id": 28434, "name": "Thibault Magni"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143959JNZ2BdqLYMj8GIwx.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p>\r\n<p>          </p>\r\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\r\n<h2>Prometeo by Paolo D’lppolito</h2>\r\n<p>意大利设计师 Paolo D’lppolito 最近设计了一款多功能的咖啡桌 <a href=\"http://www.dippo.it/en/x-portfolio/prometeo-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prometeo</a>，矮小的桌腿使它很适合放在床上陪你一起惬意地休息。它采用一种名为 Adamantx 的新型材料制成，并且在表面做了抛光处理，看上去很有光泽。咖啡桌的表面有两个方形凹槽，可以放进配套的收纳盒还有钥匙、花盆等小物件。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121624Zy9leIUnXKf6t1wq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121625fqESL93tCnWGyaw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121625I9Je3XxoqCQ4rkHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121626QNn9XlwOTJxMce73.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121626B8r0i5eO2K9XCsUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\r\n<h2>TILE by NuAns</h2>\r\n<p>如何使电子产品的使用更具灵活性并且融入生活是日本品牌 NuAns 一直致力于解决的问题，这一次他们把台灯和充电支架结合在一起推出了这款名为 <a href=\"http://nuans.jp/products/tile\" rel=\"nofollow\">TILE</a> 的产品。采用平直线条作为设计理念，TILE 优雅的流线型轮廓可以很自然地融入到周边环境之中，让人感觉就是房间的一部分。你可以通过底部的 Lightning 接口为 iPhone 或是 iPad 充电，隐藏式的设计使它能够在不使用的时候收起来。除此之外，TILE 背面还有一个 USB 接口，可以同时为两样设备充电。这是它的<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a312a.7700824.w4002-836380971.23.uPufyZ&amp;id=521901290835\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 958 元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121627cqhnuVs3b8N1APJo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121627XgBbpPw8CEKNGYO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216273DqTO4pQbetaER8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021216283yi5DbRkWpGCsNjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121628s6fCP4MUpJtqFBiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121629fUKj1tGkwsBah6Fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure></div>\r\n<h2>Energysquare by Energysquare</h2>\r\n<p>我们拥有的电子产品越来越多，充电的方式却鲜有革新。这款名为 Energysquare 的充电板想让你收起杂乱无章的充电线，轻松地为多个设备同时充电。它采用传导式专利充电技术，使用的时候只需要将配套的便签条贴到设备充电口，将设备放在充电板上就会自动进行充电。Energysquare 不仅充电速度和普通的充电器相同，表面还使用了防水设计，即使不小心沾到了液体也不用担心。如果你对它感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/700146891/energysquare-always-stay-charged\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 59 欧元。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121629dXRBWItYj9zcC4fS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121630crtwkoBZ5A426FIC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121630UwBLZzRyM67QnTWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57584683\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121631NwlqL6CtF1dpxk0s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121631aEeT3Zq9iYnHJboQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59264706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mr O hanger by Neri&amp;Hu</h2>\r\n<p>如果你喜欢极简风格的衣帽架，由中国工作室 <a href=\"http://en.neriandhu.com/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Neri&amp;Hu</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.offecct.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Offecct</a> 所设计的 Mr O hanger 会让你眼前一亮。金属经过弯曲后构成了长方形的纤细框架，由下方混凝土制成的底座支撑，在视觉上形成了鲜明的对比。框架的弧线设计减少了金属材质所带来的冰冷的感觉，看上去非常优雅。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121631hegUKb6BrQfiHvL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00138889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121632vZrz4hyMcgAa9ofl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121632qp6wD1lE3Q9xnBe2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121633kgyFXlzDsr6Kc0aA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121633fM8kgzqIcy4FW7Co.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Indefinite Vases by Studio EO</h2>\r\n<p>来自斯德哥尔摩的 <a href=\"http://studioeo.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio EO</a> 最近推出了一组名为 Indefinite Vases 的花器。经过精心设计而吹制成的玻璃容器就像是慵懒地或坐或躺在大理石制成的底座上一样，强调了空间与物体之间的关系。坚硬的石块与易碎的玻璃经过组合，带给人一种奇妙的美感。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121634ri8h1N7fWAjkxPSR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121634J6xgW9ZNh3yRs4rK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121635xe8612NGgTws35EM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121635HK2Vfs5hM0oI1SF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121636QNcTmEkt4pgPVUhI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121636An7C9LsKx0SdJoQ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>FACES by Thibault Magni</h2>\r\n<p>这个名为 FACES 的香水包装设计是加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://www.thibaultmagni.fr/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thibault Magni</a> 的作品。FACES 的晶莹剔透的瓶身就好像是电影《了不起的盖茨比》中华丽的吊灯坠饰，在金色的映衬下显得格外奢华。香水的外盒则采用了反棱镜的形状，就像是为瓶子量身打造的镀金的茧。</p>\r\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\r\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121637kcqseMEXtajm3wCD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121637KWsyZioLvNawpYhu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121638SRrlHpmIqBO61Qb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121638aUzejqPSyAEl9V72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121638NsKWnEQBjkwqIlSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702121639lJUxybsuS4RoZGVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>"}